_sText:
This is a _strafe map made for beginners. With this, I wanted to make a map that would help introduce people to the concept of _strafe maps. Please play this map as it was intended. I honestly don't see anyone having fun playing this map on auto/easy.

This map features : 
-Various jumps/paths made for people who are new to playing legit.
-A climbing bonus

I hope you guys can enjoy this map as much as I enjoyed making it. Have fun!
